They were able to help create what would be,

2593
02:17:33.395 --> 02:17:35.645
what could make transformative change.

2594
02:17:36.345 --> 02:17:37.885
Um, so we are actually appalled

2595
02:17:37.885 --> 02:17:38.885
that we would wanna remove this.

2596
02:17:38.885 --> 02:17:40.405
We don't see where any red tape is

2597
02:17:40.405 --> 02:17:42.005
because why would you not wanna

2598
