our health workforce is not feeling valued

2608
02:18:01.965 --> 02:18:03.245
and not feeling recognized.

2609
02:18:03.465 --> 02:18:05.125
And this is a big piece of work

2610
02:18:05.125 --> 02:18:06.485
that would've helped promote that.

